<p>Welcome to Sample Scripts.  Here you will find a number of pre-scripted Revolution objects, together with a detailed discussion of each script.  You can use these scripts, copy the objects into your own application, or take them apart to see how they work.  We recommend you have gone through <font face="Lucida Grande" size="11"><i>The Quick Start</i></font>, <font face="Lucida Grande" size="11"><i>Using Objects</i></font> and <font face="Lucida Grande" size="11"><i>Using Scripts</i></font> sections before trying to understand the Sample Scripts.</p>